      private static void displaySummaryList(javax.swing.JList summaryExaminationList, javax.swing.JList summaryBookingroomList, Patient patient, java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination)
      this function is update all the Examen and Chambre related to a specific Patient
      the arraySummaryExamination and arraySummaryRoom have to be clear at the beginning of the function
      A loop is used to check all of the Examen in the arrayExamination We compare the Patient stored in the Object Examen with the one in the param of the function When the values are equals the Examen is stored in arraySummaryExamination Then an Chambre Object extract the informations related to the Chambre stored in the Examen if this Object isn't null then it is stored in arraySummaryRoom
      This process is repeted as long as we haven't reach the end of arrayExamination
      Then the results are displayed in summaryExaminationList and summaryBookingroomList

        displaySummaryList
        

        private static void displaySummaryList(javax.swing.JList summaryExaminationList,
                                       javax.swing.JList summaryBookingroomList,
                                       Patient patient,
                                       java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination)
        

        this function is update all the Examen and Chambre related to a specific Patient
 
         
 the arraySummaryExamination and arraySummaryRoom have to be clear at the beginning of the function
 
         
 A loop is used to check all of the Examen in the arrayExamination
 We compare the Patient stored in the Object Examen with the one in the param of the function
 When the values are equals the Examen is stored in arraySummaryExamination 
 Then an Chambre Object extract the informations related to the Chambre stored in the Examen
 if this Object isn't null then it is stored in arraySummaryRoom
 
         
 This process is repeted as long as we haven't reach the end of arrayExamination
 
         
 Then the results are displayed in summaryExaminationList and summaryBookingroomList
 
        

        

        Parameters:
        

        summaryExaminationList - : display in a JList all the Examen whose have been registered for a patient
        

        summaryBookingroomList - : display in a JList all the informations related to the object Chambre for a patient
        

        patient - : A specific Patient object
        

        arrayExamination - : used to keep the Examen object extracted from external file or created by the user
